description: If you've ever been to San Antonio, you're probably a fan of Tripoli’s Mediterranean Grill, and you’ll be especially pleased to discover that this renowned restaurant is taking their fantastic food to the streets, via the trusty Tripoli’s Express truck. They’re serving up all the local favorites, such as their Chicken and Beef Shawarma, Chicken Tikka, Lamb Gyro Wraps & Bowls, and more.This delicious and fresh made-to-order cuisine is certainly worth a trip to Tripoli’s Express.
name: Tripoli's Express
